message:
HackerEarth and ERASE Child Trafficking, together announce the launch of the “Missing Hackathon”. The Missing Hackathon will help find new solutions to aid in law enforcement human trafficking investigations and identify missing victims faster, using technology.
https://buff.ly/2Hl31Y7
